	<div style="text-align:right;">
		BRITO, Rodrigo de<sup>1</sup>; KALINOWSKI, Alessandra<sup>2</sup>; BACK, Luiza Carla Honorio<sup>3</sup>; PREIS, Cassio<sup>4</sup>		<BR>
